## Ollama Integration

- Planner (`llm_planner.py`): local tool-calling via `requests.post(f"{OLLAMA_URL}/api/generate")`
- Vision (`vision.py`): llama3.2-vision â†’ cloud fallback
- Embeddings: `OllamaEmbeddingFunction` for ChromaDB
- Health check: `requests.get(f"{OLLAMA_URL}/api/tags")`

## RAG (rag.py)

- ChromaDB `PersistentClient` at `data/chroma/`
- Global collection + per-project collections (`project_{id}`)
- Distance threshold: `< 1.5` to inject context
- Embedding model: `nomic-embed-text` via Ollama

## Fallback Chain

Every LLM-dependent path must have fallbacks:

```
Ollama planner (local) â†’ NLU parser (no LLM) â†’ Groq/Gemini cloud â†’ offline message
```

